C++ Project using SFML, created in 2010 by Am√©lie Benoit & Romain Chabernaud


JBALL

To launch the game, go to "jball" repository and use the following commands :
Compile command : "make"
Launch game : "./JBall"

Rules : 
Try to build walls and seal off blocks without hitting walls. You have a time limit. You can build horizontal or vertical wall, change the cursor using the mouse wheel. 

Options are availables. You can press "p" key during the game to pause, and you will then be able to save the game, change the options, leave the game.

